												<h1 itemprop="headline" class="postTitle entry-title">A more humane approach to digital scholarship</h1>
						<div class='framing'><p>Can diagrams, bar charts, or network maps possibly convey the human warmth and drama of literature, religion, and history? And what happens to a researcher’s critical capacity and sensitivity when she uses a software program to study complex sources?</p>
